translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 倒し処女を奪う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeat and take the virgin

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 最期は、４０人の少女達の力を吸収し
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In the end, absorbing the power of 40 girls,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 変態化していくラギシスをなんとか倒し
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: somehow defeat Ragisys as he becomes a pervert,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: めでたしめでたし
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And they all lived happily ever after.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はにほー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hanihoo (a cheerful greeting)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 後々、関係してくる設定ポイントをまとめるよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll summarize the key points that will relate later.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 志津香、マリアとの腐れ縁とも言える関係が始まる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A fated relationship begins with Shizuka and Maria.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ウィリス、レベル神になった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Willis became the Level God.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アーシー、お菓子大好き
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Arcy loves sweets.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: バード、彼の運命もここから狂った
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Bard, his fate also went awry from here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: Ｒａｎｃｅ３　−リーザス陥落−
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance 3 - The Fall of Leazas -

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: １９９１年発売（２０１５年リメイク版０３）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Released in 1991 (2015 Remake version 03)
640*400 resolution, 16 colors, PC-98 and others.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人の力を借りたヘルマン帝国が
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Hellman Empire, borrowing the power of the demons,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リーザス王国を一晩で占領した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: occupied the Leazas Kingdom in one night.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リア王女はランスに最期の望みを託した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Princess Ria entrusted her last hope to Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: のんびり暮らすランスとシィルの元に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: To the leisurely living Rance and Shil,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リーザスを救って欲しいと忍者(かなみ)が現れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: a ninja (Kanami) appeared asking them to save Leazas.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そうしてランスは事件に巻き込まれていく
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And so Rance got involved in the incident.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 冒険者ラーク＆ノアとの出会い…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Encounter with adventurers Lark & Noah...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リスの洞窟で魔人サテラと遭遇…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Encountered the demon Satera in the Squirrel Cave...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 失った聖武具を取り戻す為に…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: To retrieve the lost sacred armor...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 悪魔を騙して悪魔回廊を通る…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Deceived demons to pass through the Demon Corridor...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カスタムの町で志津香、マリアと合流…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Met up with Shizuka and Maria in the town of Custom...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ヘルマン軍のヘンダーソンを倒す…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeated Henderson of the Hellman army...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そんなこんなの冒険をしている内に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: While going through adventures like these,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いつのまにかリーザス解放軍のリーダーとなり
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: he became the leader of the Leazas Liberation Army before he knew it,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 数千の部隊を率いてリーザスへ向かう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: leading thousands of troops toward Leazas.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人サテラにシィルが掠われたり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Shil was kidnapped by the demon Satera...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハイパービルを登ったり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Climbed Hypervil...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 烈火鉱山でヒララ鉱石を捜したり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Searched for Hirara ore in the Raging Fire Mine...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ラプの村でスーと出会ったり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Met Sue in Lap Village...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: セルさんに説教されたり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Got scolded by Mr. Sel...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いろいろな女の子を犯したり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Committed acts against various girls...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス率いるリーザス反乱軍は幾多の戦いに勝利し
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Leazas rebel army led by Rance won many battles,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ヘルマン軍を撃退し、ついにリーザス首都に到着
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: repelled the Hellman army, and finally reached the Leazas capital.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リーザス城で大決戦となる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A great battle takes place at Leazas Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 地下で魔剣カオスを手に入れる…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Obtained the magic sword Chaos underground...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人アイゼルを撃破…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeated the demon Aizel...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: このまま解放戦争に勝利するかと思われたが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It seemed like they would win the liberation war,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人達の目的はリーザス地下に封印されていた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but the demons' true goal was the being sealed under Leazas,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王ジルを復活させる事だった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: to resurrect the Demon King Jill.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 最期の一踏ん張りでランス達は
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: With a final push, Rance and his group

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人ノスを撃破…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: defeated the demon Nos...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王ジルを再び封印…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and sealed Demon King Jill again...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こうして、魔人とヘルマンからリーザスを救い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Thus, they saved Leazas from the demons and Hellman,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 救国の英雄となるが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: becoming heroes who saved the country,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 異空間にて光の神を踏んでしまい飛ばされる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but stepped on the God of Light in another dimension and were transported away.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・・・めでたしめでたし？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...And so, happily ever after?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はにほー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hanihoo.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 後々、関係してくる設定ポイントをまとめるよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll summarize key points related later.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リーザスの救国の英雄となる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Became the hero who saved Leazas.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔剣カオスの所有者となる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Became the owner of the magic sword Chaos.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ３体の魔人を倒した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeated three demons.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マリア、チューリップ３号を開発する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Maria developed Tulip No.3.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 志津香、かなみ、ミル、一緒に冒険する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Shizuka, Kanami, and Mill adventure together.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パットン、駄目王子として登場、駄目なまま退場
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Patton appeared as a useless prince and exited still useless.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: Ｒａｎｃｅ４　−教団の遺産−
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance 4 - The Heritage of the Cult -

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: １９９３年発売
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Released in 1993

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 倒し処女を奪う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeat and take the virgin

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 最期は、４０人の少女達の力を吸収し
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In the end, absorbing the power of 40 girls,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 変態化していくラギシスをなんとか倒し
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: somehow defeat Ragisys as he becomes a pervert,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: めでたしめでたし
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And they all lived happily ever after.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はにほー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hanihoo (a cheerful greeting)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 後々、関係してくる設定ポイントをまとめるよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll summarize the key points that will relate later.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 志津香、マリアとの腐れ縁とも言える関係が始まる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A fated relationship begins with Shizuka and Maria.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ウィリス、レベル神になった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Willis became the Level God.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アーシー、お菓子大好き
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Arcy loves sweets.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: バード、彼の運命もここから狂った
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Bard, his fate also went awry from here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: Ｒａｎｃｅ３　−リーザス陥落−
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance 3 - The Fall of Leazas -

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: １９９１年発売（２０１５年リメイク版０３）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Released in 1991 (2015 Remake version 03)
640*400 resolution, 16 colors, PC-98 and others.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人の力を借りたヘルマン帝国が
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Hellman Empire, borrowing the power of the demons,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リーザス王国を一晩で占領した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: occupied the Leazas Kingdom in one night.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リア王女はランスに最期の望みを託した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Princess Ria entrusted her last hope to Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: のんびり暮らすランスとシィルの元に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: To the leisurely living Rance and Shil,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リーザスを救って欲しいと忍者(かなみ)が現れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: a ninja (Kanami) appeared asking them to save Leazas.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そうしてランスは事件に巻き込まれていく
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And so Rance got involved in the incident.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 冒険者ラーク＆ノアとの出会い…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Encounter with adventurers Lark & Noah...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リスの洞窟で魔人サテラと遭遇…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Encountered the demon Satera in the Squirrel Cave...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 失った聖武具を取り戻す為に…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: To retrieve the lost sacred armor...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 悪魔を騙して悪魔回廊を通る…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Deceived demons to pass through the Demon Corridor...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カスタムの町で志津香、マリアと合流…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Met up with Shizuka and Maria in the town of Custom...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ヘルマン軍のヘンダーソンを倒す…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeated Henderson of the Hellman army...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そんなこんなの冒険をしている内に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: While going through adventures like these,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いつのまにかリーザス解放軍のリーダーとなり
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: he became the leader of the Leazas Liberation Army before he knew it,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 数千の部隊を率いてリーザスへ向かう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: leading thousands of troops toward Leazas.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人サテラにシィルが掠われたり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Shil was kidnapped by the demon Satera...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハイパービルを登ったり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Climbed Hypervil...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 烈火鉱山でヒララ鉱石を捜したり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Searched for Hirara ore in the Raging Fire Mine...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ラプの村でスーと出会ったり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Met Sue in Lap Village...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: セルさんに説教されたり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Got scolded by Mr. Sel...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いろいろな女の子を犯したり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Committed acts against various girls...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス率いるリーザス反乱軍は幾多の戦いに勝利し
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Leazas rebel army led by Rance won many battles,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ヘルマン軍を撃退し、ついにリーザス首都に到着
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: repelled the Hellman army, and finally reached the Leazas capital.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リーザス城で大決戦となる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A great battle takes place at Leazas Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 地下で魔剣カオスを手に入れる…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Obtained the magic sword Chaos underground...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人アイゼルを撃破…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeated the demon Aizel...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: このまま解放戦争に勝利するかと思われたが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It seemed like they would win the liberation war,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人達の目的はリーザス地下に封印されていた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but the demons' true goal was the being sealed under Leazas,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王ジルを復活させる事だった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: to resurrect the Demon King Jill.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 最期の一踏ん張りでランス達は
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: With a final push, Rance and his group

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人ノスを撃破…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: defeated the demon Nos...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王ジルを再び封印…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and sealed Demon King Jill again...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こうして、魔人とヘルマンからリーザスを救い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Thus, they saved Leazas from the demons and Hellman,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 救国の英雄となるが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: becoming heroes who saved the country,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 異空間にて光の神を踏んでしまい飛ばされる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but stepped on the God of Light in another dimension and were transported away.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・・・めでたしめでたし？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...And so, happily ever after?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はにほー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hanihoo.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 後々、関係してくる設定ポイントをまとめるよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll summarize key points related later.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リーザスの救国の英雄となる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Became the hero who saved Leazas.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔剣カオスの所有者となる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Became the owner of the magic sword Chaos.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ３体の魔人を倒した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeated three demons.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マリア、チューリップ３号を開発する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Maria developed Tulip No.3.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 志津香、かなみ、ミル、一緒に冒険する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Shizuka, Kanami, and Mill adventure together.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パットン、駄目王子として登場、駄目なまま退場
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Patton appeared as a useless prince and exited still useless.
